{"tid":419352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日如期出發　乘客擔心滯留當地","createTime":"2017-09-30T12:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T12:16:16.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9bac8e7e793ec97e48f2ae7a2db46a2f2859a0cf","tid":419352,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00001/31ce4f4e01221e3a4caf7bf4b485dedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F31ce4f4e01221e3a4caf7bf4b485dedb.jpg&h=fe49c3d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（賴俊傑攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00001/3105b1e7a9830fa273bd505b8fa992db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F3105b1e7a9830fa273bd505b8fa992db.jpg&h=dd541ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊先生指今次事件影響對廉航的信心，下次外遊時會考慮其他航空公司。（賴俊傑攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00001/310b2905ee4a26ea4f970dd834a453bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F310b2905ee4a26ea4f970dd834a453bc.jpg&h=cc2bafe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孫小姐表示選擇乘搭香港快運是因為價錢便宜，故日後亦會繼續乘搭。（賴俊傑攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00001/310a06eca6037d3898b9f4c5e96ee500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F310a06eca6037d3898b9f4c5e96ee500.jpg&h=649c87c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳小姐表示，如果在黃金周這關鍵時間發生類似事件，將會破壞航空公司的誠信，日後也很難立足。（賴俊傑攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00001/31e6edf8b8673b91c48404d0f21914c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F31e6edf8b8673b91c48404d0f21914c6.jpg&h=53d1ccbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機場內香港快運的櫃枱。(賴俊傑攝)<br />\n<br />\n香港快運航空公司突然取消明日(10月1日)起至10月8日往返香港與日本大阪、名古屋及韓國首爾的18定期航班，乘客「人人自危」，有今日出發前往日韓的乘客如期啟程，但擔心回程航班會被取消、滯留當地。<br />\n<br />\n今日飛往大阪的楊先生稱，原定下月10日回程，昨晚得悉事件後，即時上網查詢自己的航班資料，發現沒有受影響，但仍然擔心回程航班會被取消或延誤。楊指前往亞洲、東亞南等地方，多選擇乘搭廉航，但今次事件影響他對廉航的信心，下次外遊時會考慮其他航空公司。<br />\n<br />\n飛往首爾、原定10月8日返港的孫小姐，至今沒有收到航空公司通知，但她擔心會滯留當地，當初選擇乘搭香港快運是因為價錢便宜，故日後亦會繼續乘搭。<br />\n<br />\n同樣飛往首爾、原定10月8日返港的內地遊客陳小姐則說，雖然行程沒有受到影響，但對事件感到十分震驚，直言如果自己是受害者，影響到一年一次的黃金周假期，一定會爭取到底。她又表示，如果在黃金周這關鍵時間發生類似事件，將會破壞航空公司的誠信，日後也很難立足。<br />\n<br />\n12月經「縱橫遊」跟團前往首爾的陳小姐稱，屆時將乘搭快運航班，對於今次事件，快運已有後備方案，國泰亦會提供協助，所以現時不會太擔心。她說今次是第一次乘搭快運，認為若跟團出發，一旦發生任何事故，都有旅行社協助，所以哪間航空公司都沒有問題，但如果自由行，「寧願多付一點錢，買個安心」，不會選購快運等廉航公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170930/s00001/1506757035388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F1506757035388&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=03653b19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F1506757035388&h=07298558\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170930/s00001/1506757035388</a>"},{"pid":"3c69efeb515329c88ade31cd9c0c1fbd2181d0ff","tid":419352,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00001/31ce4f4e01221e3a4caf7bf4b485dedb.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F31ce4f4e01221e3a4caf7bf4b485dedb.jpg%22&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2b5d77b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F31ce4f4e01221e3a4caf7bf4b485dedb.jpg%22&h=66ac9b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00001/31ce4f4e01221e3a4caf7bf4b485dedb.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n（賴俊傑攝）<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930